msgstr "解锁互斥锁。"

#: ../../library/mutex.rst:75
msgid ""
"Try to acquire the mutex in a non-blocking way. Return ``True`` on "
"success and ``False`` on failure."
msgstr "尝试以非阻塞方式获取互斥锁。成功返回 ``True``，失败返回 ``False``。"

#: ../../library/mutex.rst:77
msgid "You may also acquire the mutex in a blocking way by using ``with``."
msgstr "您也可以使用 ``with`` 以阻塞方式获取互斥锁。"
